extends /layouts/default

block content
    section.banner
        .container.content-bottom
            .content-box
                h1(data-animation="reveal") Get Your Garden Summer<br/> Ready: Organize with<br/> Rothley Storage Solutions!
        .bg
            img.image(src="/images/news/banner-2.png", alt="image")

    section.content-section.reverse
        figure.content-figure(data-animation="reveal")
            img.image(src="/images/news/image-2.png", alt="image")

        .content-box(data-animation="reveal" data-animation-delay="100")
            h2 Get Your Garden Summer Ready: Organize with Rothley Storage Solutions!
            p As the weather gets sunnier and longer, it’s natural to start thinking about those delightful summer BBQs with friends and family. To make the most of the season, it’s important to get your garden in top shape.
            p
                | This is the perfect time for a thorough clean of your garden, refreshing the outdoor space and clearing away the clutter and grime that accumulates during the Winter months.&nbsp;
                a(href="/") Rothley’s range of storage solutions
                |  can be your ally in organizing your tools and equipment efficiently. In this blog, we’ll share valuable tips on effectively sprucing up your garden for the summer season while you simplify storage with Rothley’s storage solutions.

    section.news-content-three
        .container
            .content-list
                .list-item(data-animation="reveal")
                    .content-box
                        h6 Plan for a Summer-Ready Garden
                        p The first step towards a successful summer garden is to create a plan. Take a walk around your garden and assess which areas require attention. Make a list of tasks that need to be accomplished and prioritize them. To ensure a well-organized garden and garden shed, consider incorporating Rothley’s range of storage solutions. From twin-slot shelving units to storage and utility hooks, you’ll find plenty of options to help you maximize space and keep your tools neatly stored away.
                    figure.content-figure
                        img.image(src="/images/news/image-3.png", alt="image")
                .list-item(data-animation="reveal")
                    .content-box
                        h6 Declutter for a Refreshed Garden
                        p Before diving into the summer preparations, it’s essential to declutter your garden. Go through each area and remove any unnecessary items that may be cluttering the space. This includes old pots, broken furniture, and unused equipment. Clearing out the clutter will not only enhance the appearance of your garden but also make it easier to maintain during the Summer months.
                    figure.content-figure
                        img.image(src="/images/news/image-3.png", alt="image")
                .list-item(data-animation="reveal")
                    .content-box
                        h6 Efficient Storage Solutions for Outdoor Tools
                        p Is your garden shed or storage area in need of a makeover? Now is the perfect time to optimize your storage options. Look for practical storage systems that can adapt to your needs. Rothley offers adjustable shelves that can be repositioned, allowing you to create custom storage configurations for your gardening essentials. Whether it’s tools, pots, or supplies, Rothley’s shelving brackets and systems will help you keep everything organized and easily accessible.
                    figure.content-figure
                        img.image(src="/images/news/image-3.png", alt="image")
                .list-item(data-animation="reveal")
                    .content-box
                        h6 Secure and Store for a Safe, Summer-Ready Garden
                        p During your Summer preparations, you may come across tools or equipment that require repair. Take the time to address these repairs to ensure everything is in working order. Once completed, store tools that are not frequently used in your garage or a designated storage unit, keeping them safely out of the way.
                        p For added safety, utilize Rothley’s storage and utility hooks to secure potentially hazardous tools and prevent accidents. Make use of often-overlooked spaces, such as the back of doors, to keep clutter at bay. Install hanging baskets, storage cubes, or spring clips to make the most of this vertical space and keep your garden essentials neatly stored away.
                    figure.content-figure
                        img.image(src="/images/news/image-3.png", alt="image")

            .news-box.content-box(data-animation="reveal")
                p Getting your garden Summer ready is an exciting endeavour that can be achieved with the help of Rothley Storage Solutions. By following these tips, you’ll be well-prepared to enjoy a beautiful and organized garden throughout the Summer season. Get ready to embrace the outdoors and create lasting memories with family and friends in your perfectly arranged and Summer-ready garden.
                p If you have any additional inquiries regarding the Rothley product range, don’t hesitate to contact one of our Laydex team members today for assistance!
                .news-bottom
                    p.paragraph-sm Share this post:
                    .btns
                        a.social-link(href="/")
                            img.icon(src="/icons/fb.svg", alt="image")
                        a.social-link(href="/")
                            img.icon(src="/icons/ln.svg", alt="image")
                        a.social-link(href="/")
                            img.icon(src="/icons/insta.svg", alt="image")


    +type-section
